commit.message: Updated changelog for 2.3.0 and 2.3.1
v2.3.1 - Updated dependencies, fixed bug with checking table row id
Fixed bug where loop wasn't checking for empty string id
Updated sqlite3 because prior version didnt work with node10
Updated dependencies to fix security vulnerabilities
Version 2.3.0 - Added caching of Rate My Professors data
Implemented SQLite caching of RMP data
changed sql query to get info from rmp_cache table
Created table in db to cache RMP info
Handled comma in regex parsing of the names
Added updated db with 2018 data
Version 2.2.0 - Sentiment analysis and algorithm changes
Took sentiment into account and changed average weighting
Fixed link to Longhorn logo for loading icon
Added how algorithm works
Version 2.1.0 - Took difficulty and take again percentage into account
Fix algorithm to make higher difficulty a lower score
Removed unnecessary logging

Took difficulty and take again metrics into account in score calculation

- Added average of rating, difficulty, and take again metrics to average GPA for score

- Minor style fixes (using inner functions)

- Fixed bug in which score was calculated as average GPA * 2 if at least one professor was on RMP
Minor style fixes
Added scraping of difficulty and take again percentage
Scraping method returns object instead of just rating
Version 2.0.3 - Bug fix when no profs on RMP
Fixed case where none of profs are on RMP
Fixed version in package
Course value now case insensitive

Merge pull request #3 from sandeepnamburi/backend-rewrite

Rewrote backend with promises instead of callbacks
